    <string name="worker_puzzle_help_title">Worker puzzle</string>
    <string name="worker_puzzle_help_text">The goal of this puzzle is to choose the optimal worker action to start the game given your starting location and tiles.\n\nThe optimal action will be the one that improves the value of your best tile. Your priorities should be food, shields, then commerce, in that order.\n\nIn these puzzles, you\'re in Despotism, so mind the Despotism penalty which will reduce any outputs greater than two by one.\n\n\To solve the puzzle:\n\t1. Select a tile\n\t2. Choose a worker action\n</string>
    <string name="worker_puzzle_intro_text">Choose the optimal worker action to start the game given your starting location and tiles.\n\nThe optimal action will improve the value of your best tile. Your priorities should be food, shields, then commerce, in that order. However, if you already have plenty of food output, it is better to increase production.\n\nMind the Despotism penalty, which will reduce any outputs greater than two by one.</string>

